    p Cards, along with List View, is a one more great way to contain and organize your information. Cards contains unique related data, for example, a photo, text, and link all about a single subject. Cards are typically an entry point to more complex and detailed information.
    p Card Vue component represents <a href="../docs/cards.html">Cards</a> component.
