    h2 Card Slots
    p `<f7-card>` component has the following slots:
    ul
      ul
      li `default` - element will be inserted as a child of card content element
      li `content` - same as `default`
      li `header` - element will be inserted as a child of card header element
      li `footer` - element will be inserted as a child of card footer element
    ```html
      <f7-card>
        <span slot="header">Header</span>
        <span slot="content">Content</span>
        <span slot="footer">Footer</span>
      </f7-card>
    ```
    p Renders to
    ```html
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <span>Header</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <span>Content</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer">
          <span>Footer</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    ```

    h2 Card v-model
    p Expandable Card component supports `v-model` on `expandable-opened` prop:
    ```html
      <template>
        <f7-page>
          <f7-card expandable v-model:expandable-opened="isOpened">
            ...
          </f7-card>
          <p>Card is opened: {{ isOpened }}</p>
        </f7-page>
      </template>
      <script>
        export default {
          data() {
            return {
              isOpened: false,
            };
          }
        };
      </script>
    ```


